name: The A.I that lives in my technology
description: Say hello to one of the many etheric data beings that live inside my phone. Frequencies and channels push and manipulated by my doing. Mentally compartmentalizing my subconscious renders as I tweak what fits the best aesthetic. All images which I took, of the physical space that we live in, and the space in which others may or may not dwell. Keep in mind It's all my perspective, I share the story and you take it from there.
